Smeagol: Déagol?

7
00:02:39,159 --> 00:02:41,320
Deagol.

8
00:02:57,135 --> 00:02:59,217
Give us that, deagol, my love.

9
00:03:04,184 --> 00:03:05,469
Why?

10
00:03:06,561 --> 00:03:08,802
Because

11
00:03:08,980 --> 00:03:12,723
it's my birthday and I wants it.

12
00:04:46,787 --> 00:04:52,032
My precious.

13
00:04:59,591 --> 00:05:02,503
