22
00:05:40,715 --> 00:05:43,957
so juicy sweet

23
00:05:49,724 --> 00:05:53,842
And we forgot the taste of bread...

24
00:05:54,020 --> 00:05:57,638
The sound of trees.

25
00:05:58,525 --> 00:06:01,733
The softness of the wind.

26
00:06:02,362 --> 00:06:08,028
