27
00:06:16,167 --> 00:06:22,584
My precious.

28
00:07:06,843 --> 00:07:09,084
Wake up!

29
00:07:10,138 --> 00:07:11,799
Wake up!

30
00:07:11,973 --> 00:07:13,759
Wake up, sleepies.

31
00:07:13,934 --> 00:07:15,799
We must go, yes.

32
00:07:15,977 --> 00:07:18,639
We must go at once.

33
00:07:22,192 --> 00:07:25,275
