35
00:07:31,409 --> 00:07:33,149
Must be getting late.

36
00:07:33,328 --> 00:07:34,818
Frodo: No.

37
00:07:34,996 --> 00:07:36,907
It isn't.

38
00:07:37,082 --> 00:07:40,119
It isn't midday yet.

39
00:07:40,293 --> 00:07:42,375
The days are growing darker.

40
00:07:47,133 --> 00:07:49,340
Come on!

41
00:07:51,763 --> 00:07:54,004
Must go! No time!

42
00:07:54,182 --> 00:07:56,548
Not before Mr. Frodo's
had something to eat.

43
00:07:56,726 --> 00:07:59,593
Gollum: No time to lose, silly.

44
00:08:08,363 --> 00:08:09,648
Sam: Here

45
00:08:12,867 --> 00:08:14,698
what about you?

46
00:08:14,869 --> 00:08:18,236
Oh, no, I'm not hungry.
Leastways, not for lembas bread.

47
00:08:18,832 --> 00:08:20,197
Sam.

48
00:08:22,794 --> 00:08:24,330
All right.

49
00:08:24,504 --> 00:08:26,995
We don't have that much left.

50
00:08:27,173 --> 00:08:30,040
