or we're going to run out.

51
00:08:32,220 --> 00:08:35,132
You go ahead and eat that, Mr. Frodo.

52
00:08:35,306 --> 00:08:36,716
I've rationed it.

53
00:08:37,225 --> 00:08:38,886
There should be enough.

54
00:08:41,062 --> 00:08:42,268
For what?

55
00:08:43,940 --> 00:08:45,680
The journey home.

56
00:08:53,533 --> 00:08:55,865
Gollum: Come, hobbitses.

57
00:08:57,245 --> 00:08:59,110
Very close now.

58
00:08:59,289 --> 00:09:02,531
Very close to mordor.

59
00:09:02,709 --> 00:09:05,371
No safe places here.

60
00:09:05,545 --> 00:09:07,706
Hurry.

61
00:10:00,100 --> 00:10:01,806
Merry: It's good.

62
00:10:02,727 --> 00:10:04,467
Definitely from the shire.

63
00:10:06,689 --> 00:10:08,805
Longbottom leaf.

64
00:10:14,155 --> 00:10:18,489
I feel like I'm back at
the green dragon.

65
