- A mug of ale in my hand.

66
00:10:22,997 --> 00:10:27,582
Putting my feet up on a settle
after a hard day's work.

67
00:10:28,169 --> 00:10:31,627
Only, you've never done
a hard day's work.

68
00:10:44,435 --> 00:10:47,472
Welcome, my lords...

69
00:10:47,647 --> 00:10:49,888
To isengard!

70
