of isengard.

78
00:11:24,225 --> 00:11:27,217
Treebeard: Young master Gandalf.

79
00:11:27,395 --> 00:11:31,980
I'm glad you've come.

80
00:11:32,150 --> 00:11:36,564
Wood and water, stock and stone
I can master.

81
00:11:36,738 --> 00:11:40,401
