00:22:09,995 --> 00:22:13,078
Merry & pippin:
But the only brew for the brave and true

200
00:22:13,415 --> 00:22:15,451
comes from the green dragon

201
00:22:18,796 --> 00:22:21,629
merry: Thank you! I win!

202
00:22:23,425 --> 00:22:25,916
No news of Frodo?

203
00:22:26,095 --> 00:22:29,587
No word. Nothing.

204
00:22:30,432 --> 00:22:32,593
We have time.

205
00:22:34,103 --> 00:22:37,391
Every day, Frodo moves closer to mordor.

206
00:22:38,107 --> 00:22:40,189
Do we know that?

207
00:22:44,029 --> 00:22:45,769
What does your heart tell you?

208
00:22:52,788 --> 00:22:56,121
That Frodo is alive.

209
00:22:58,294 --> 00:23:00,125
Yes

210
00:23:02,673 --> 00:23:04,664
yes, he's alive.

211
00:23:07,136 --> 00:23:09,969
Gollum: Too risky. Too risky.

212
00:23:10,139 --> 00:23:11,345
Thieves.

213
00:23:11,515 --> 00:23:13,551
They stole it from us.

214
00:23:13,726 --> 00:23:16,809
Kill them. Kill them. Kill them both.

215
00:23:18,564 --> 00:23:22,148
Shh! Quiet! Mustn't wake them.

216
00:23:22,318 --> 00:23:24,809
Mustn't ruin it now.

217
00:23:24,987 --> 00:23:27,069
But they knows.

218
00:23:27,239 --> 00:23:29,150
They knows.

219
00:23:29,325 --> 00:23:31,941
They suspects us.

220
00:23:33,162 --> 00:23:36,654
What's it saying, my precious, my love?

221
00:23:36,832 --> 00:23:40,450
Is smeagol losing his nerve?

222
00:23:41,086 --> 00:23:43,498
No. Not.

223
00:23:43,672 --> 00:23:47,881
Never. Sméagol hates nasty hobbitses.

224
00:23:48,052 --> 00:23:52,887
Smeéagol wants to see them dead.

225
00:23:53,057 --> 00:23:55,594
And we will

226
00:23:55,768 --> 00:23:59,852
