He means to murder us.

259
00:25:58,307 --> 00:26:02,471
Never! Sméagol wouldn't hurt a fly.

260
00:26:04,480 --> 00:26:06,516
He's a horrid, fat hobbit...

261
00:26:06,690 --> 00:26:08,305
Who hates smeéagol...

262
00:26:08,484 --> 00:26:11,226
And who makes up nasty lies.

263
00:26:11,403 --> 00:26:14,110
You miserable little maggot!
I'll stove your head in!

264
00:26:14,490 --> 00:26:15,730
Sam!

265
00:26:16,158 --> 00:26:17,694
Sam:
Call me a liar? You're a liar!

266
